---
// BeforeAfter component - shows what we're NOT vs what we ARE
---

<section class="animate space-y-6">
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">
      We're Not Another Generic Job Board
    </h5>
    <p class="text-black/50">
      No more wondering "Do they sponsor?" No more generic applications disappearing into the void. Just real opportunities, real contacts, and real results.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <!-- What we're NOT -->
    <div class="relative group flex flex-col py-6 px-6 rounded-lg border border-black/15 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-lg text-red-600">❌</span>
        </div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black">
          What we're NOT
        </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            A platform with 100,000 outdated postings
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            Another "FAANG-only" job list
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            A bot scraping Indeed and calling it "curation"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- What we ARE -->
    <div class="relative group flex flex-col py-6 px-6 rounded-lg border border-black/15 hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-lg text-emerald-600">✅</span>
        </div>
        <h6 class="font-semibold text-black">
          What we ARE
        </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            Weekly intel from someone who actually cares about your visa status
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            Focus on startups and growing companies (they need you more than you need them)
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
            Real research, real contacts, real opportunities
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 